se xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Apr 20, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xkk1665703006949.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xkk1665703006949.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xkk1665703006949.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xkk1665703006949\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"xkk1665703006949___componentinfo_254926\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return information about a component instance.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"xkk1665703006949__topic_d81038e1_d81039e1_d81040e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xkk1665703006949__p_d81041e1_d81042e1_d81043e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$componentinfo</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">InstanceName</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">TopicName</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"xkk1665703006949__section_w3013ab1b7b5_w3014ab1b7_w3015ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xkk1665703006949__p_d81044e1_d81045e1_d81046e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">$componentinfo(\"MYINSTANCE\",\"VARIABLES\")</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xkk1665703006949__topic_d53382e1_d53383e1_d53384e1_d53385e1_d53386e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d502069e90\">Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"xkk1665703006949__table_d8108e1_d8109e1_d8110e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xkk1665703006949__table_d8108e1_d8109e1_d8110e1__entry__1\">Parameter</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xkk1665703006949__table_d8108e1_d8109e1_d8110e1__entry__2\">Data Type</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xkk1665703006949__table_d8108e1_d8109e1_d8110e1__entry__3\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xkk1665703006949__table_d8108e1_d8109e1_d8110e1__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">InstanceName</var></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xkk1665703006949__table_d8108e1_d8109e1_d8110e1__entry__2\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xkk1665703006949__table_d8108e1_d8109e1_d8110e1__entry__3\">Name of the component instance.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xkk1665703006949__table_d8108e1_d8109e1_d8110e1__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">TopicName</var></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xkk1665703006949__table_d8108e1_d8109e1_d8110e1__entry__2\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xkk1665703006949__table_d8108e1_d8109e1_d8110e1__entry__3\">\n Keyword specifying the type of information to return; one of:\n <ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xkk1665703006949__li_d33770e1_d33771e1_d33772e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"VARIABLES\"</code>—list component variables for the specified component instance\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xkk1665703006949__li_d33773e1_d33774e1_d33775e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"OUTERENTITIES\"</code>—list the names of outer entities of the specified component instance\n </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\">The topic name is not case-sensitive.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xkk1665703006949__topic_d53387e1_d53388e1_d53389e1_d53390e1_d53391e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d502069e173\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xkk1665703006949__p_d81053e1_d81054e1_d81055e1\">Returns a list as specified by the <var class=\"keyword varname\">TopicName</var>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xkk1665703006949__p_d81056e1_d81057e1_d81058e1\">If an error occurs, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains a negative value that identifies the exact error.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"xkk1665703006949__table_d8111e1_d8112e1_d8113e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> Commonly Returned Following\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$componentinfo</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xkk1665703006949__table_d8111e1_d8112e1_d8113e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xkk1665703006949__table_d8111e1_d8112e1_d8113e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">Error constant</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xkk1665703006949__table_d8111e1_d8112e1_d8113e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">Meaning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xkk1665703006949__table_d8111e1_d8112e1_d8113e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-1105</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xkk1665703006949__table_d8111e1_d8112e1_d8113e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_INSTANCE&gt;</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xkk1665703006949__table_d8111e1_d8112e1_d8113e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">The instance name provided is not\n                        valid. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xkk1665703006949__table_d8111e1_d8112e1_d8113e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-1110</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xkk1665703006949__table_d8111e1_d8112e1_d8113e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_TOPIC&gt;</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xkk1665703006949__table_d8111e1_d8112e1_d8113e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">Topic name not known. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xkk1665703006949__topic_d53392e1_d53393e1_d53394e1_d53395e1_d53396e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d502069e263\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xkk1665703006949__p_d81062e1_d81063e1_d81064e1\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fsr1705402622485.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Component Instances</a><p>A component instance is a runtime version of a Uniface or non-Uniface component. It is possible to have multiple instances of the same component running simultaneously.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fgl1704695956444.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Related Component Entities</a><p>Entities are related if they are defined in a relationship in the application model. When used in components, related entities must be nested inside each other so that Uniface can enforce the relational integrity. Uniface understands that the primary key of the one entity is also the foreign key of the many entity, and synchronizes updates for you.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533759\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533759\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$componentinfo Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 20, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Return information about a component instance. $componentinfo ( InstanceName , TopicName ) Example: $componentinfo(\"MYINSTANCE\",\"VARIABLES\") Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description InstanceName String Name of the component instance. TopicName String Keyword specifying the type of information to return; one of: \"VARIABLES\" —list component variables for the specified component instance \"OUTERENTITIES\" —list the names of outer entities of the specified component instance The topic name is not case-sensitive. Return Values Returns a list as specified by the TopicName . If an error occurs, $procerror contains a negative value that identifies the exact error. Table 2. Values of $procerror Commonly Returned Following $componentinfo Value Error constant Meaning -1105 <UPROCERR_INSTANCE> The instance name provided is not valid. -1110 <UPROCERR_TOPIC> Topic name not known. Use Allowed in all component types. Related Links Component Instances A component instance is a runtime version of a Uniface or non-Uniface component. It is possible to have multiple instances of the same component running simultaneously. Related Component Entities Entities are related if they are defined in a relationship in the application model. When used in components, related entities must be nested inside each other so that Uniface can enforce the relational integrity. Uniface understands that the primary key of the one entity is also the foreign key of the many entity, and synchronizes updates for you. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}